{"tid":1019884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【患癌都可健身】確診腦癌或剩5年命 用12星期變大隻仔","createTime":"2019-02-13T08:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T04:53:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5de0d92d4cfa235fbb240ac33db617c9037b5090","tid":1019884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190210/large/1549802865_87a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190210%2Flarge%2F1549802865_87a6.jpg&h=a7f01e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國康沃爾郡（Cornwall）一名患上腦癌的健身教練，前年確診時被告知可能剩下數年命。他不但沒有放棄，反而想以最佳身體狀態對抗病情及鼓勵其他人，後來展開為期12星期的地獄式訓練，成功減掉10公斤及練出一身好身型。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【健康●國際專欄】減肥計劃必須要「親民」<br />\n<br />\n現年22歲的喬伊特（Ollie Jowett）在2017年9月確診患上惡性腦瘤，可能只剩下5年命，當時他才剛搬到北愛爾蘭貝爾法斯特（Belfast）展開他一直夢寐以求的私人教練事業。2017年尾他的身體狀況轉差，未能承受長時間工作，要縮減自己的訓練。<br />\n<br />\n不過，喬伊特拒絕因為病情而減卻他對健身的熱情，他更開始了12周地獄式訓練，利用一對一的網上個人訓練。他希望透過訓練配合飲食，以最佳的身體狀況抗癌，同時鼓勵其他人不要放棄。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【不只是玩具】19歲少年天生無手臂 用Lego自己砌出義肢<br />\n<br />\n他的故事在網頁「Ultimate Performance」上公開，其中在「你又有甚麼藉口？」頁面中，喬伊特說明自己如何利用他的病「作為他訓練的動力，激勵他的客戶，同時展示出即使面對癌症，世事皆有可能」。他指為期12周的訓練是他一生中最困難的日子，他每天都想過放棄，又指有些日子身體會很虛弱，上樓梯或外出買東西都感到困難。<br />\n<br />\n喬伊特的病令他有時會一整天臥床不起，但他會向明白他感受的教練訴說自己的情況，他堅信道：「我從一開始就知會扭轉自己的情況。生活不會停下來，我沒有為自己感到難過，因為每人都有自己的問題要處理&hellip;&hellip;我相信每人都有一個目的。我明白自己正受癌症困擾，但我現在的目的就是感染其他人及提升對癌症的認識。」"},{"pid":"a7f8e0ba3aab8c2bded224a5b744027e8e528acc","tid":1019884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190213/59243505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190213%2F59243505&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=5a9edc34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190213%2F59243505&h=18daaa23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190213/59243505</a>"},{"pid":"c7851a9b208d6399eb38c966ac8f990516977607","tid":1019884,"uid":236401,"like":5,"dislike":84,"score":-79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6e0352ef596239793ec361b86138f50db9a8ce2","tid":1019884,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7851a9b208d6399eb38c966ac8f990516977607","tid":1019884,"uid":236401,"like":5,"dislike":84,"score":-79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568320d08339a44470cda3852a141e6fbf7397f5","tid":1019884,"uid":151865,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"c7851a9b208d6399eb38c966ac8f990516977607","tid":1019884,"uid":236401,"like":5,"dislike":84,"score":-79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"佢無頭腦無心志四肢係唔會發達"},{"pid":"54b209c748d2674c6e8d8cdae5e5fcdb3355612b","tid":1019884,"uid":121473,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"唔係應該留點體力去同病魔打，仲谷到咁地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f2272f1c90421266a3a7f2cbc82c8f12c04c6a","tid":1019884,"uid":121866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"腦癌都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37310e49ff042c58b3b07438a16282afdcf2d761","tid":1019884,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7851a9b208d6399eb38c966ac8f99051